{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/svrr9rwhc07g9sih/","result":{"data":{"sitePage":null},"pageContext":{"url":"posts/svrr9rwhc07g9sih","relativePath":"posts/svrr9rwhc07g9sih","frontmatter":{"title":"没想到李一舟翻车了，但我不管，仍然在向李一舟们学习","stackbit_url_path":"posts/svrr9rwhc07g9sih","date":"2024-02-26T11:44:02","excerpt":"","tags":[],"categories":[],"template":"post"},"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.08108108108108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/829b75f69538d5010e971b5b6b49213b/fcda8/1708921005618-988d7682-cf1e-4114-9fb2-d64c2283e943.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/829b75f69538d5010e971b5b6b49213b/12f09/1708921005618-988d7682-cf1e-4114-9fb2-d64c2283e943.png 148w,\n/static/829b75f69538d5010e971b5b6b49213b/e4a3f/1708921005618-988d7682-cf1e-4114-9fb2-d64c2283e943.png 295w,\n/static/829b75f69538d5010e971b5b6b49213b/fcda8/1708921005618-988d7682-cf1e-4114-9fb2-d64c2283e943.png 590w,\n/static/829b75f69538d5010e971b5b6b49213b/96658/1708921005618-988d7682-cf1e-4114-9fb2-d64c2283e943.png 881w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<a name=Z43vH></a></p>\n<h1>这张图片还有人没看到过吗？</h1>\n<p>我最早是在 2 月 19 日从一个微信群里看到的，有人还不认识右边的人是谁，而我是他的粉丝，并在群里科普。<br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/43ddca2a11d639bb5d2649ef77fd73a1/d9199/1708920958263-df8068b9-e493-4bb3-a6d7-ef4a53c9bf38.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 187.83783783783784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/43ddca2a11d639bb5d2649ef77fd73a1/fcda8/1708920958263-df8068b9-e493-4bb3-a6d7-ef4a53c9bf38.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/43ddca2a11d639bb5d2649ef77fd73a1/12f09/1708920958263-df8068b9-e493-4bb3-a6d7-ef4a53c9bf38.png 148w,\n/static/43ddca2a11d639bb5d2649ef77fd73a1/e4a3f/1708920958263-df8068b9-e493-4bb3-a6d7-ef4a53c9bf38.png 295w,\n/static/43ddca2a11d639bb5d2649ef77fd73a1/fcda8/1708920958263-df8068b9-e493-4bb3-a6d7-ef4a53c9bf38.png 590w,\n/static/43ddca2a11d639bb5d2649ef77fd73a1/efc66/1708920958263-df8068b9-e493-4bb3-a6d7-ef4a53c9bf38.png 885w,\n/static/43ddca2a11d639bb5d2649ef77fd73a1/d9199/1708920958263-df8068b9-e493-4bb3-a6d7-ef4a53c9bf38.png 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>没想到，之后就到处看到那张经典的图片，将他和奥特曼放在一起。随后的事情让我大跌眼镜，所说他的视频课程被下架，并有网友亲测退费秒到账。最魔幻的是央视也点他名了，总之，李一舟似乎被封杀了。\n<a name=VVojr></a></p>\n<h1>读者中有人买过他的课程吗？</h1>\n<p>我之所以关注他，是因为我经常刷短视频，并经常刷到他。而他的分析问题头头是道，逻辑满分，就关注了，我还在朋友圈分享过他的视频。<br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a42b7418b29e7044772c1f203b585deb/d9199/1708921428687-1025195a-bd8f-44c3-9e17-e53c796ee25e.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 216.89189189189187%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/a42b7418b29e7044772c1f203b585deb/fcda8/1708921428687-1025195a-bd8f-44c3-9e17-e53c796ee25e.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a42b7418b29e7044772c1f203b585deb/12f09/1708921428687-1025195a-bd8f-44c3-9e17-e53c796ee25e.png 148w,\n/static/a42b7418b29e7044772c1f203b585deb/e4a3f/1708921428687-1025195a-bd8f-44c3-9e17-e53c796ee25e.png 295w,\n/static/a42b7418b29e7044772c1f203b585deb/fcda8/1708921428687-1025195a-bd8f-44c3-9e17-e53c796ee25e.png 590w,\n/static/a42b7418b29e7044772c1f203b585deb/efc66/1708921428687-1025195a-bd8f-44c3-9e17-e53c796ee25e.png 885w,\n/static/a42b7418b29e7044772c1f203b585deb/d9199/1708921428687-1025195a-bd8f-44c3-9e17-e53c796ee25e.png 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>不过，我没有买他的 AI 课程。每次刷到他的所谓 AI 课程“直播”，我就刷走了。因为他好像是在教如何使用 AI 做 PPT 之类的小技巧，我对这些没有兴趣。并不是对 AI 没有兴趣，是对 PPT 之类的没有兴趣。相反，我对 AI 很有兴趣，并且在“极客时间”上订阅了很多 AI 课程。<br />除了李一舟卖 AI 课程之外，我还注意到我关注了很久的“鹤老师”也在卖 AI 课程，套路和李一舟差不多，都是用“录播”方式来直播，话术也一样，还剩最后几个名额等等。但可能卖得不如李一舟多吧，所以文章开头的照片上，放的是李一舟而不是鹤老师。<br />同样的，每次刷到鹤老师的 AI 课程，我会直接划走。\n<a name=n0UmW></a></p>\n<h1>我买了鹤老师的新商业思维课</h1>\n<p>虽然我没有购买两位老师的 AI 课程，但是我很早就购买了鹤老师的新商业思维课程。我之前也分享过鹤老师的视频对我的启发：《<a href=\"%5Bhttps://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/603609077%5D(https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/603609077)\">鹤老师：真正的知识是体系 - Jeff Tian的文章 - 知乎</a> 》。<br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 112.83783783783782%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/5a00470cf5ce5f59ac7f455f9ffec7ec/fcda8/1708944864419-e5f3e87f-3eb5-4cbd-a898-7ffc8e27d67d.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5a00470cf5ce5f59ac7f455f9ffec7ec/12f09/1708944864419-e5f3e87f-3eb5-4cbd-a898-7ffc8e27d67d.png 148w,\n/static/5a00470cf5ce5f59ac7f455f9ffec7ec/e4a3f/1708944864419-e5f3e87f-3eb5-4cbd-a898-7ffc8e27d67d.png 295w,\n/static/5a00470cf5ce5f59ac7f455f9ffec7ec/fcda8/1708944864419-e5f3e87f-3eb5-4cbd-a898-7ffc8e27d67d.png 590w,\n/static/5a00470cf5ce5f59ac7f455f9ffec7ec/efc66/1708944864419-e5f3e87f-3eb5-4cbd-a898-7ffc8e27d67d.png 885w,\n/static/5a00470cf5ce5f59ac7f455f9ffec7ec/d9199/1708944864419-e5f3e87f-3eb5-4cbd-a898-7ffc8e27d67d.png 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span><br />399 的课程，是李一舟 AI 课程的两倍。听大家都在说李一舟的 AI 课程很水，但我觉得鹤老师的新商业思维课程却很值。当然，这也是见仁见智的，比如我相信薛兆丰就不会购买鹤老师的这门课程，就像我不会购买他们的 AI 课程一样。<br />说起薛兆丰，我也在得到上购买了他的经济学课。<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 216.2162162162162%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/63c9204cc54486a8ac50b9c355169070/fcda8/1708945144907-09b287ff-3875-4f16-9225-1c14aa7e047d.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/63c9204cc54486a8ac50b9c355169070/12f09/1708945144907-09b287ff-3875-4f16-9225-1c14aa7e047d.png 148w,\n/static/63c9204cc54486a8ac50b9c355169070/e4a3f/1708945144907-09b287ff-3875-4f16-9225-1c14aa7e047d.png 295w,\n/static/63c9204cc54486a8ac50b9c355169070/fcda8/1708945144907-09b287ff-3875-4f16-9225-1c14aa7e047d.png 590w,\n/static/63c9204cc54486a8ac50b9c355169070/efc66/1708945144907-09b287ff-3875-4f16-9225-1c14aa7e047d.png 885w,\n/static/63c9204cc54486a8ac50b9c355169070/78797/1708945144907-09b287ff-3875-4f16-9225-1c14aa7e047d.png 1125w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>尽管也非常有启发，但我必须得说，鹤老师的课程对我启发更大，于是我又还买了鹤老师的两本书。<br />我花了 399 购买的鹤老师的视频课程，我刷了两遍，<strong>上次分享过一些碎片，今天再分享一次吧</strong>。刷两遍，分享两次，没毛病。\n<a name=zmVKg></a></p>\n<h1>核心权重</h1>\n<p>这是我的弱项，总是抓不到重点。就是《教父》中的经典名言：在半秒钟内看透本质的人，和一辈子都看不透本质的人，注定有两种命运。<br />鹤老师说的核心权重，就是这种看到本质的能力，这也是一种判断力。<br />工作中我就碰到有人很会抓到核心权重，这也是为什么他们短时间就能获得晋升的原因。有一次和老板去饭店吃饭，被问到如果你是这家店的老板，你会看重什么指标？我支支吾吾语无伦次。老板说，记住了，是“翻台率”，做为饭店老板，就要盯着翻台率；做为我们公司，就应该怎样怎样……。<br />我听了之后感觉自愧不如。<br />罗振宇在 2024 年跨年演讲中提到一个学校，学生饱受课间时间太短之苦，有时候老师拖堂，10 分钟被占掉好几分钟，结果搞到连上厕所都来不及。这个学校的校长只用了一招，就解决了这个问题：那就是将课间 10 分钟改成了 5 分钟。就这一招，连带性地带来了各种改变，也是一个能够抓住核心权重，化繁为简的高人。\n<a name=QfGYD></a></p>\n<h1>什么是财富自由？</h1>\n<p>这个问题，如果抓不到核心权重，会给出一大堆答案但都只是隔靴搔痒。鹤老师的课程里讲，财富自由是效率的碾压。你挣 100 万需要一年或者两年的时间，但另一个人只需要 1 到 2 天的时间，这就是效率的碾压。\n<a name=OWPTW></a></p>\n<h1>为什么短视频火了？</h1>\n<p>短视频并不是时间短，而是信息密度大。总之，就是提高了你的信息获取效率，所以才火。\n<a name=xs3gB></a></p>\n<h1>短视频的核心权重是什么？</h1>\n<p>完播率。这是他通过换位思考得出的结论。如果你是平台，你会怎么分发流量？当然，这个完播率得在同样的类型的视频中相对比较才有效。\n<a name=HWHHd></a></p>\n<h1>做短视频要不要买流量？</h1>\n<p>一般人之所以做短视频，就是因为通过其他途径赚钱慢，而短视频赚钱更快。所以买流量就是站不住脚的。或者这样说，钱、流量以及时间，它们都是等价的。你拍了视频想获得流量，要么花更多时间，创作出好内容，从而不用花钱也有流量。要么花钱直接买流量，那么你节省了创作的时间。<br />为什么你不应该花钱买流量呢？因为你的时间没那么值钱，所以才需要创作好内容去换流量也就是钱。谁应该花钱买流量呢？那些富豪们，就是赚钱效率更高的人可以花钱买流量。\n<a name=DeFna></a></p>\n<h1>反思：不应该过度营销</h1>\n<p>虽然李一舟翻车了，但仍然有这样的李一舟们还在。他们逻辑清晰，并且有很多碎片化的输出免费给到大家，我还是愿意向他们学习的。只要内容好，花钱也值。<br />但是李一舟们的确存在过度营销的问题，有些事情（比如转化率）做到所谓“极致”，会让人反感。很多公司其实都存在这样的问题，毕竟只有提高转化率，才能养活公司和员工嘛。<br />有时候通过 A/B 测试，验证某一新功能的确带了营收增长，的确值得嘉奖。这就是李一舟们反复“录播”，以及一直说“还有最后几个名额”的原因，他们验证了这样带来转化率是最高的。但也许不必要在一味追求增长的方向上不懈努力，稍微躺平一点不好吗？卖得太多，超出了消费者们本来的需要，总感觉让人有些不舒服。<br />鹤老师，也是在说你呢，我很早就发现你所谓的抓紧时间拍，几分钟后恢复原价之类的，其实第二天还是可以 399 买下来的。虽然你的课程内容让我满意，但是也希望再改进一下，不要光追求转化率，还是得真实一点，好吗？</p>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","author":"@zizhujy","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageedit_3_2509022194.png","background_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7m0jrKYaDBwEvlc5lo8nt6/6d50a5050d9cdc0d4d2047e35feac292/10648733_696750647079056_2800539603462658695_o.jpg","has_nav":true,"nav_links":[{"label":"Home","url":"/","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"About","url":"/about","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"关于","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/about","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"Contact","url":"/contact","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"Support Me","url":"/support-me","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"叽叽歪歪","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_window":true,"type":"action"}],"has_social":true,"social_links":[{"label":"Twitter","url":"https://twitter.com/zizhujy","style":"icon","icon_class":"fa-twitter","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"Instagram","url":"https://www.instagram.com/jefftian5","style":"icon","icon_class":"fa-instagram","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"GitHub","url":"https://github.com/jeff-tian","style":"icon","icon_class":"fa-github","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"LinkedIn","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/jeff~tian","style":"icon","icon_class":"fa-linkedin","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"DEV","url":"https://dev.to/jefftian","style":"icon","icon_class":"fa-dev","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"知乎","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/jefftian","style":"icon","icon_class":"fa-zhihu","new_window":true,"type":"action"}],"type":"header"},"footer":{"content":"&copy; All rights reserved.","links":[{"label":"Made with Stackbit.","url":"https://www.stackbit.com","style":"link","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"紫竹叽歪","url":"https://zizhujy.apphb.com","style":"link","icon_class":"http://zizhujy.apphb.com/Content/Images/logo.png","new_window":true,"type":"action"}],"type":"footer"}},"pathPrefix":"","data":{"data":{"author":{"name":"Jeff Tian","avatar":"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--a5qDZLv3--/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_640,q_auto,w_640/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/318420/3bfd2d99-430c-4049-8dd5-e2adc961e1e0.png"},"social":{"devto":{"username":"jefftian"},"twitter":{"username":"zizhujy"},"github":{"username":"Jeff-Tian"}}}}},"menus":{}}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}